<headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 21 at 6:51PM CDT until June 21 at 7:30PM CDT by NWS Houston - Galveston</headline>
<description>The National Weather Service in League City has issued a
* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Southwestern Houston County in southeastern Texas...
Madison County in southeastern Texas...
* Until 730 PM CDT.
* At 650 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located over Austonio,
moving southeast at 45 mph.
HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.
SOURCE...Radar indicated.
IMPACT...Hail damage to vehicles is expected. Expect wind damage
to roofs, siding, and trees.
* Locations impacted include...
Madisonville, Austonio, Lovelady, Normangee and North Zulch.
HAIL THREAT...RADAR INDICATED
MAX HAIL SIZE...1.00 IN
WIND THREAT...RADAR INDICATED
MAX WIND GUST...60 MPH</description>
<instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
